Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d1", "Hello newcomer. I know there's a lot to absorb around here, I can help you get started.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d2", "Who are you?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d3", "My name is Heavensgate. Ex-red at your service. With the exterminators, talk to those around here to learn more.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d4", "What do you want to help me with?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d5", "Well, there's a new resource around these areas. We're not sure how it got here or what it really is, but we have an affinity for it.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d6", "Elaborate.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d7", "We here have been calling it \"Ancient Gas\", or just \"Gas\" for short. It's been around since the first of us were abandoned.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d8", "Where can I find it?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d9", "It's found as swirling vortices. We've seen them scattered in sectors in no specific pattern. However, vortices are much larger in DeadZones for some reason.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d10", "How do I extract it?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d11", "By literally wading into it. It appears we absorb the stuff out of vortices automatically! No idea why. It appears wading closer to the core gets you more.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d12", "Do you know any sectors where I can find some?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d13", "Yep, I can mark them on the map for you. In fact, let's give you a little mission to get some.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d14", "Okay...")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d15", "Marked one sector on your map. Come back with 100 gas -- note that entering the center of a vortex will kill you, and death will always take 100 gas away from you!")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_start_d16", "Gotta be careful then.")
