Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d1", "Congrats! It's fun to wade into the vortices but some don't like the risk of being disassembled. I guess it's an acquired taste.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d2", "What do I do with this resource?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d3", "Well, we've discovered two uses. Abilities seem to be \"boostable\" with gas, with unique enhancements if you let them drain some over time.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d6", "What else can I do with gas?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d7", "There's also Part Fusion. I can help you with that too.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d8", "...")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d9", "Why don't we go to your base? I can help you set up the Fusion Station needed for this.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d10", "Okay, I'll meet you there...")


Text("GGG_heavensgate_postCollection_d4", "To GAS BOOST your abilities, Ctrl-click them. GAS BOOSTED abilities slowly drain GAS over time.")


