Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d1", "...and when you unharness their core energy you should attach stabilizers beforehand, not after the fact. It's harder at first but the rest becomes easier and you get used to it.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d2", "...")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d3", "Hmm... probably should've thought of that before...")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d4", "I see you've acquainted yourselves with each other.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d5", "Ah, there you are! We've already set up the Fusion Station. Now for me to explain how to use it.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d6", "Go on...")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d7", "You can combine the part type of one part and the ability of another into one at this station. Best part about it is that it marks the entry for that part on your index!")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d8", "Fusing parts requires Fusion Energy, which can be made with gas and shards. Unlike gas, you don't lose Fusion Energy if you are killed!")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d9", "You'll need more Fusion Energy to create parts with higher-tier abilities or when you fuse parts with different size categories.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d10", "Why don't you try fusing two parts together? I'll give you a cool new ability you can only find here if you do.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_FS_d11", "Okay...")


