Text("GGG_heavensgate_postFS_d1", "Nice going! Fusion can be really handy when trying to create powerful parts for tough combat situations.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postFS_d2", "Why are you being so helpful to us?")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postFS_d3", "Want me to be honest? We need more recruits to join the exterminators! But I'd have no hard feelings if you choose not to join.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postFS_d4", "Anyway, that's really all there is to gas! Congrats. Here's your new ability.")
Text("GGG_heavensgate_postFS_d5", "Thanks!")

